        <tocItem href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ssi/2017/72/code-of-practice/1/paragraph/19" level="2"><inline name="tocHeading">19. Steps to be taken immediately after a search</inline></tocItem>
        <tocItem href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ssi/2017/72/code-of-practice/1/paragraph/20" level="2"><inline name="tocHeading">20. Searches which do not result in an arrest</inline></tocItem>
        <tocItem href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ssi/2017/72/code-of-practice/1/paragraph/21" level="2"><inline name="tocHeading">21. Searches which result in an arrest</inline></tocItem>
        <tocItem href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ssi/2017/72/code-of-practice/1/paragraph/22" level="2"><inline name="tocHeading">22. Notes for guidance</inline></tocItem>
        <tocItem href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ssi/2017/72/code-of-practice/1/paragraph/23" level="2"><inline name="tocHeading">23. Recording</inline></tocItem>
        <tocItem href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ssi/2017/72/code-of-practice/1/paragraph/24" level="2"><inline name="tocHeading">24. ANNEX A</inline></tocItem>
        <tocItem href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ssi/2017/72/code-of-practice/1/paragraph/25" level="2"><inline name="tocHeading">25. List of main statutory powers of Stop and Search of the person</inline></tocItem>
        <tocItem href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ssi/2017/72/code-of-practice/1/paragraph/26" level="2"><inline name="tocHeading">26. (note: other statutory powers of search may also exist)</inline></tocItem>
        <tocItem href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ssi/2017/72/code-of-practice/1/paragraph/27" level="2"><inline name="tocHeading">27. ANNEX B</inline></tocItem>
        <tocItem href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ssi/2017/72/code-of-practice/1/paragraph/28" level="2"><inline name="tocHeading">28. Establishing Gender of Persons for the Purpose of Searching</inline></tocItem>
        <tocItem href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ssi/2017/72/code-of-practice/1/paragraph/29" level="2"><inline name="tocHeading">29. Consideration</inline></tocItem>
        <tocItem href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ssi/2017/72/code-of-practice/1/paragraph/30" level="2"><inline name="tocHeading">30. Searching of Transgender Persons</inline></tocItem>
        <tocItem href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ssi/2017/72/code-of-practice/1/paragraph/31" level="2"><inline name="tocHeading">31. ‘Is there anything I need to know before I search you?’</inline></tocItem>
        <tocItem href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ssi/2017/72/code-of-practice/1/paragraph/32" level="2"><inline name="tocHeading">32. Documentation</inline></tocItem>
        <tocItem href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ssi/2017/72/code-of-practice/1/paragraph/33" level="2"><inline name="tocHeading">33. Disclosure of information</inline></tocItem>
        <tocItem href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ssi/2017/72/code-of-practice/1/paragraph/34" level="2"><inline name="tocHeading">34. Notes for Guidance</inline></tocItem>
        <tocItem href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ssi/2017/72/code-of-practice/1/paragraph/35" level="2"><inline name="tocHeading">35. ANNEX C</inline></tocItem>
        <tocItem href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ssi/2017/72/code-of-practice/1/paragraph/36" level="2"><inline name="tocHeading">36. CONDUCT OF STRIP AND INTIMATE SEARCHES</inline></tocItem>
        <tocItem href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ssi/2017/72/code-of-practice/1/paragraph/37" level="2"><inline name="tocHeading">37. A: Strip search</inline></tocItem>
        <tocItem href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ssi/2017/72/code-of-practice/1/paragraph/38" level="2"><inline name="tocHeading">38. Action</inline></tocItem>
        <tocItem href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ssi/2017/72/code-of-practice/1/paragraph/39" level="2"><inline name="tocHeading">39. The conduct of strip searches</inline></tocItem>
        <tocItem href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ssi/2017/72/code-of-practice/1/paragraph/40" level="2"><inline name="tocHeading">40. B: Intimate search</inline></tocItem>
        <tocItem href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ssi/2017/72/code-of-practice/1/paragraph/41" level="2"><inline name="tocHeading">41. Action</inline></tocItem>
        <tocItem href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ssi/2017/72/code-of-practice/1/paragraph/42" level="2"><inline name="tocHeading">42. Documentation</inline></tocItem>
